From 3333582f854dff58fc83bde58cde9746fe75b9f5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 11:27:40 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(security+bugs): lock admin panel, fix categories/shop
 bugs, wire real payment gateways

Security:
- Protect all /admin routes with verifyAdmin (was completely public)
- Fix verifyAdmin: roles is an array (use includes), verify single fitrix_token
  cookie with the USER secret (matches admin login signing)
- Restrict admin login to users whose roles include ADMIN/SUPER_ADMIN
- Fix isGuest roles array check; fix globalData selecting roles (was role)

Bugs:
- Categories: createSubCategories used non-existent 'name' field and wired
  parent/child backwards -> now sets title/slug/parent and links child into
  parent.subCategories
- Shop filters/sort used wrong field names -> priceSingle/quantity/viewsCount/soldCount
- productSingle: handle missing product (404) and exclude self from related; count view
- product router: register /categories before /:slug so it is reachable

Payment gateways:
- New payment.service.js: Zarinpal (SDK) + Digipay (OAuth) request/verify,
  env-driven with safe mock fallback when keys are not configured
- createPayment/verifyPayment now use real gateway request + verification
- Add gateway env vars to .env.example

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_019fhmuc7ZofnhXQGM2EDkKu
